                            <comment id="13215433" author="hustlmsp" created="Fri, 24 Feb 2012 06:37:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;attach a patch to delay ledger directories creation.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13215441" author="hustlmsp" created="Fri, 24 Feb 2012 06:44:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;we did a simple performance testing comparing non-delay-dir-creation and delay-dir-creation.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;3 bookie server, ensemble size 3, quorum size 2:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test steps:&lt;br/&gt;
1) create &lt;/p&gt;
{num} ledgers&lt;br/&gt;
2) add 2 * {num}
&lt;p&gt; message to these ledgers in round-robin way (so a new message of each ledger would be added to each bookie server)&lt;br/&gt;
3) compute the throughput number&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;the result is shown as below&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;table class=&apos;confluenceTable&apos;&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th class=&apos;confluenceTh&apos;&gt;num&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th class=&apos;confluenceTh&apos;&gt; 1,000 &lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th class=&apos;confluenceTh&apos;&gt; 10,000 &lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th class=&apos;confluenceTh&apos;&gt; 100,000 &lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th class=&apos;confluenceTh&apos;&gt; 1,000,000 &lt;/th&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt; non-delay-dir-creation &lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt; 3,154.57 &lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt; 4,564.71 &lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt; 4,618.40 &lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt; 10,468.79 &lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt; delay-dir-creation &lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt; 4,219.41 &lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt; 7,401.92 &lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt; 16,636.17 &lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt; 18,267.00 &lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
</comment>
